# User-defined dictionary overrides for ru-normalizr.
# Format:
# source=replacement
#
# `*` is supported in source patterns as a wildcard for non-space characters.
# This file is an example only and is not packaged into the wheel.
#
# Examples:
# *Tube=тюб
# Open*=оупен
# YouTube=ютуб
# OpenAI=оупэнэйай
########################################################################################
# You can add .dic files to this folder and rules would be applied automatically
